<br>
I don't think server-wide events are going to ever come to fruition when left in the hands of individuals, or at least most of them.  With some guild participation something really nice might be worked out.<br>
<br>
I'm a bit low level now to do any fighting, but I'd love to come to the Arena to see some nice fights among Resolution and any others that showed up.  You could charge people admission - a low rate to watch, and a higher rate to participate based on level (I saw one tournament with 2xlvl in plat as an admission fee) and then give a portion of that to the winner, a smaller portion to the runner up, maybe even a third place, and possibly some door prize raffles of some nice gear that guilds might be hoarding.<br>
<br>
*sigh*  I can't wait to get higher in level so I can apply to some guilds, become involved in things. <p>Shiden
