      Your idea about turning the server into a Sullon Zek for a day or two, or even a week, would be so AWESOME!  Such an event would add to the flavor and developing history of the server.  As you said, war on a massive scale followed by peace would create many tales of heroism and folly that would most definitely be integrated into people's roleplaying.  Your sugesstion so impressed me that I would add this:<br>
Why not stage a war like that once every month and a half, or when political tensions run high in a given area? (like right now between the Tier'dal and the Council of Light) As a result of such an event, newbie characters and those who play their characters as loners would have a hand in shaping the history of the server.<br>
<br>
Pass the word if you can, and watch all of the &quot;true&quot; roleplayers flock to this server!  <br>
